                     <interp inst="t18630406-599-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing a watch, value 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18630406-name-266" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18630406-name-266" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
